{"tid":2460930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清算未跟抵制「新疆」棉花品牌解約明星　Angelababy陳奕迅有份","createTime":"2021-03-25T06:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T06:35:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"80a35478c7ad6727e3bc0514df9e53b10c86004b","tid":2460930,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:29:10.000Z","msg":"在H&amp;M的聲明中，提及了一個名為「瑞士良好棉花發展協會（Better Cotton Initiative，BCI）」的組織，當中聲稱，BCI已決定暫停在新疆發放BCI棉花許可證，因此H&amp;M產品所需要的棉花將不再從那裡獲得。據悉，BCI組織成員眾多，包括NIKE、adidas、PUMA、Tommy Hilfiger、BURBERRY、IKEA等，繼H&amp;M集團之後，NIKE、adidas、New Balance、Gap、ZARA等都紛紛發表聲明抵制新疆棉花，而NIKE的兩位代言人王一博、譚松韻也在第一時間解約。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210325/451740770798407680751049.jpeg/v5d9T11qm411-iI2hdP3F1KdP1Gx2F29jbv0e4279Hs?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210325%2F451740770798407680751049.jpeg%2Fv5d9T11qm411-iI2hdP3F1KdP1Gx2F29jbv0e4279Hs%3Fv%3Dw640&h=3464b59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚松韻終止同NIKE合作。（微博@兩小姐的便利貼）<br />\n<br />\n然而，有網友列出該組織中的其他品牌代言人，認為他們尚未解約，似乎想要清算，倪妮、Angelababy、王嘉爾、陳奕迅、劉亦菲、吳謹言、古力娜扎、劉雯、易烊千璽、鄧倫等在列，引起網友熱議，有人不停施壓，希望這些藝人快點出聲明，而也有人認為應該給點時間，畢竟解約不是一個人的事，有很多利益牽扯，不要盲目追究明星等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210325/451744154376998912714250.jpeg/r1ze1AxZu9Vfobmz6_QOaJ2F41nlh8R6z_1AEM_9QBA?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210325%2F451744154376998912714250.jpeg%2Fr1ze1AxZu9Vfobmz6_QOaJ2F41nlh8R6z_1AEM_9QBA%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=1aad22b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01. com/即時娛樂/603936</code></pre>"},{"pid":"9e79b331fdbe94fd5dbbd4c0e6d2c4927ec6c384","tid":2460930,"uid":98473,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"提還提 唔好提陳奕迅 張敬軒<br />\n依兩個唔係奶共 係搵食 唔計嫁<br />\n其他人先係奶共"},{"pid":"88b1f4639b5cde5a6dce8a5ac14921b09fc2c533","tid":2460930,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e79b331fdbe94fd5dbbd4c0e6d2c4927ec6c384","tid":2460930,"uid":98473,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"提還提 唔好提陳奕迅 張敬軒<br />\n依兩個唔係奶共 係搵食 唔計嫁<br />\n其他人先係奶共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:33:14.000Z","msg":"張敬軒係廣州仔，廣州人有幾多會反共呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d0ba99a0b8e18e9fe8d0573b6a32055e56151e","tid":2460930,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e79b331fdbe94fd5dbbd4c0e6d2c4927ec6c384","tid":2460930,"uid":98473,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"提還提 唔好提陳奕迅 張敬軒<br />\n依兩個唔係奶共 係搵食 唔計嫁<br />\n其他人先係奶共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:33:23.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅已經變咗支那藝人喇"},{"pid":"0e1b679ac2da6af254ea6468176a83d5aa631d62","tid":2460930,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e79b331fdbe94fd5dbbd4c0e6d2c4927ec6c384","tid":2460930,"uid":98473,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"提還提 唔好提陳奕迅 張敬軒<br />\n依兩個唔係奶共 係搵食 唔計嫁<br />\n其他人先係奶共"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"賺藍錢有咩問題？"},{"pid":"60b6f3ddb55b4d8a3cc7bbb106558b50dbe87e1f","tid":2460930,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:34:16.000Z","msg":"易烊千璽<br />\n咩名黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02624cd5cada9f2c33f052723e59933146d8aad0","tid":2460930,"uid":22210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRbhtkNVxw53v3mg4tNCgyFPnjvTJSYYVWdyXP4xdm4aE?filename=e5VFqme.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5VFqme.png&h=fb1c0974&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8d337a639d422afe3f6a3013ecc83fae5316e15","tid":2460930,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e1b